{"tid":1657703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美報告指中国透過黑客間諜　自煮燃發C919發動機技術","createTime":"2019-10-16T08:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T08:27:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e9bdc1e5f0a81c2c9a8be59761ab9f3f93f235fd","tid":1657703,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1486493_1_L_20191016141000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1486493_1_L_20191016141000.jpg&h=2f00ccb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（法新社資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n美國一家網絡安全公司發表報告，指控中國政府透過黑客及間諜，以及國家指示，來填補關鍵技術和情報的空缺，從而製造出渦輪發動機，協助由中國商用飛機公司研製的C919客機，與飛機製造商波音及空中巴士競爭。<br />\n<br />\n報告顯示，由2010年至2015年，江蘇省國家安全廳的相關人員通過使用惡意軟件，攻擊多家航空工業公司，同時又派出間諜，進行情報搜集工作，雖然有多人被美國當局以涉嫌從事黑客活動拘捕，但報告認為，事件不會阻止北京繼續進行這種黑客和間諜活動，用以推動具有戰略意義領域的躍進式發展。<br />\n<br />\n報告表示，C919客機仍然面臨很大的阻礙，需要獲取國際認證，以及面對中美貿易戰。報告認為，中美貿易談判是否會限制北京通過中外合資、強制技術轉移、人工間諜活動以及網路盜竊等手段，繼續加速航空工業發展，目前仍有待觀察。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486493-20191016.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486493-20191016.htm&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVgogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=8d8fe971\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486493-20191016.htm&h=d83c8c02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486493-20191016.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1428012e4703b4497a936e53d328ddef7c4ae2e6","tid":1657703,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:12:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afoWPNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafoWPNY.jpg&h=041452ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4e4e5c174a77e91eab2160d7ce01370f6f3dfe71","tid":1657703,"uid":46966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自整諗啦仆街 成日想偷人野"},{"pid":"f065791d89dfd75f2a4d363ec6cff91e0850f73b","tid":1657703,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:18:20.000Z","msg":"屌佢個引擎做撚到出黎未姐⋯"},{"pid":"9383f403f672812f7c39934834498d512187c5f9","tid":1657703,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:21:23.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n辛苦製作，求手足幫推！！！"},{"pid":"6d237b52c80339913e3fa05ca821c9468deeb52a","tid":1657703,"uid":173002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:27:17.000Z","msg":"暴政鐵係海外投資鐵路，係安裝訊號系統時加裝竊聽器，可為強國取得機密情報幫上忙，大家唔好阻礙黨鐵係歐美澳洲嘅鐵路投標呀。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}